TLVParse is a Java library that can be used to convert a Java object into its TLV 
representation. It can also be used to convert a TLV bytes into an 
equivalent Java object. TLVParser can work with arbitrary Java objects including 
pre-existing objects that you do not have source-code of.

Complete Gson documentation is available at its project page 
https://github.com/zcmilan/TLVParse
